headline: Accenture Named a Leader in Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Digital Technology and Business Consulting Services
summary: NEW YORK, January 15, 2026--Accenture was recognized as a Leader in the inaugural Gartner, Inc. "Magic Quadrant for Digital Technology and Business Consulting Services" report.

headline: ManageEngine Is Named a Challenger in the 2026 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Endpoint Management Tools, scoring above 4/5 across all 4 Use Cases
